  "id": "019ce976-18fc-7ba0-8290-1e68a308ff7b",
  "content": "# Dashboard UX Overhaul — Implementation Summary (2026-03-13)\n\n## What Was Built\n18 tasks across 5 chunks, all completed and pushed.\n\n### Chunk 1: ClusterStore Foundation\n- K-means clustering with k-means++ initialization on 768-dim embeddings\n- Silhouette scoring for optimal K selection (K=3..12)\n- ClusterHierarchy with SuperCluster → sub-cluster → member hierarchy\n- 15 unit tests in clustering.rs\n\n### Chunk 2: Graph LOD + Agent Enrichment\n- Multi-tiered LOD rendering (L0-L3) with zoom-driven level switching\n- Viewport culling replacing 500-edge hard limit\n- Breadcrumb navigation for drill-down context\n- Agent cards with description, topic pills, drift indicator\n- GET /api/dashboard/graph/scope (clustered response)\n- GET /api/dashboard/agents/reconnectable\n- POST /api/dashboard/agents/{agent_id}/connect\n- POST /api/dashboard/agents/{agent_id}/refresh-summary\n\n### Chunk 3: Activity Feed + History Rewrite\n- GET /api/dashboard/activity — semantic grouping, content deltas, topic tags\n- HistoryView completely rewritten from UUID-lookup to activity feed consumer\n- Topic filter pills, agent dropdown, \"+N more\" group expansion\n- 8 unit tests in activity.rs\n\n### Chunk 4: Cross-Tab Navigation + Agent Identity\n- SidebarAPI with navigateToHistory() for cross-tab deeplinks\n- `corvia agent connect` CLI command\n- SessionStart hook for agent identity reminder\n- Collapsible sidebar (collapsed/narrow/wide) with context-aware content\n\n### Chunk 5: Verification\n- GC confirmed to already preserve agent records (no changes needed)\n- Playwright browser verification: Graph LOD (7 super-clusters), History feed (100 entries), sidebar transitions, agent cards, config panel\n- All Tier 1 tests pass (433+)\n\n## New Endpoints Added\n- GET /api/dashboard/activity\n- GET /api/dashboard/graph/scope (enhanced with clustering)\n- GET /api/dashboard/agents/reconnectable\n- POST /api/dashboard/agents/{agent_id}/connect\n- POST /api/dashboard/agents/{agent_id}/refresh-summary\n\n## New Files\n- crates/corvia-server/src/dashboard/clustering.rs\n- crates/corvia-server/src/dashboard/activity.rs\n- .claude/hooks/agent-check.sh\n\n## Key Commits\n- corvia repo: 5a82921..857ad42 (9 commits)\n- workspace repo: 6221804..b722d7d (6 commits)",
